      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARK MONEY (1) clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 4.5 lengths second behind Blue Rudd in 18.68. Going well and rates on top. NO EYE CONTACT (4) was below best at her last start when 7th at this track following a third place finish (18.81) there two back. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Has ability and can measure up. BAUXITE LASS (2) gave a start after a chequered run when hampered to finish a 9 length seventh (23.89) at this track in a Maiden. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Must include in calculations. CORLESS SNEAKY (8) makes debut for the Tayt Corless kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can feature with the right run.",
